<plot>This film chronicles the life of William "Wop" May, one of Canada's greatest pilots. Starting with his close shave as the target of The Red Baron, this film covers Wop's colorful career as a bush pilot. The featured anecdote is of Wop May's perilous flight to transport vital medicine to an epidemic stricken community.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?092410</url></doc>
